      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DEE DEE EXPRESS (1) appreciated the jump in trip second-up with a courageous second to the progressive Dirtballer over 1200m at this track. Gets the claim again from the low gate and will take holding out. FOREIGN ENCOUNTER (2) warmed up late when the race was all over on resumption with a close-up fifth over 1200m at this track. Lone win came second-up and will be ridden for luck from the wide gate. SHUTTERING (5) is close to her peak now third-up and has the ability to finish over the top of these. Returned good closing splits when third over 1200m at this track. Leading player. JIMMY'S READY (7) returned for his second prep with a plugging fourth over 1080m at Canberra Acton in C1 grade. Looking for this trip now and worth thought.",
